{"title":"崭新的征途  献给中国共产党第十二次代表大会","authors":["何鹰"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"崭新的征途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给中国共产党第十二次代表大会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从那，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四条毒蛇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬伤了我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国母亲的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肌体；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百废待兴的山河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九百六十万平方公里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍茫大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴、发奋与崛起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在呼唤着飞跃啊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柜台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在呼唤着充实；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在呼唤着新犁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族的脊梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扳动了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的道岔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调整的连杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立刻牵动了一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的世纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从喉咙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到马达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐进出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋进的歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到责任田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时萌生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片新绿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忧心忡忡的纪念碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬眉吐气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这古老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而又巨大的龙体；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也象在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用力地扭动着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的骨节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似要腾空飞舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直上天际！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十亿人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进军的旋律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起交响成欢呼十二大的乐曲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大批，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝阳般的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中青年干部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新时代的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起跑线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隆隆飞转的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是重新加了油的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家机器；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主的绿茵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正为我们的制度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"输送着氧气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象减了肥的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那般精悍干练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身朝气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用坚定的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈进的脚步声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响亮地回答着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思在《共产党宣言》中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列出来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的试题——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义一定要胜利！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}